s:7:"keyword";s:29:"chairman of the board meeting";s:4:"slug";s:29:"chairman-of-the-board-meeting";s:5:"title";s:131:"Editable Sample Invitation Letter Stakeholders Meeting New Within Email Template For Meeting Invitation Best Professional Templates";s:3:"alt";s:9:"pinterest";s:3:"url";s:76:"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/b7/ae/5d/b7ae5d877fc0b5d98af410fc52bd8e78.jpg";s:5:"thumb";s:90:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRq_LewKmzFu--aQIteyIYjKiq9rAFZoHbX4w";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:1579;s:6:"height";i:1116;s:6:"source";s:49:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/763923155537752941/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:37:{i:0;s:80:"People who chair board meetings must deal with many different personality types.";i:1;s:88:"Openness and humility are a couple of important attributes that board chairpersons need.";i:2;s:160:"These attributes will help them hear all sides of arguments allowing opinions to come forth naturally and respectfully and creating a collaborative environment.";i:3;s:51:"Chairman of Board Meeting Under Companies Act 2013.";i:4;s:98:"A meeting of the Board to be valid must be properly constituted with a proper person in the Chair.";i:5;s:52:"The Chairman of the Board generally takes the chair.";i:6;s:43:"If there is no Chairman of the Board or he.";i:7;s:61:"The chairpersons role in a board meeting is hugely important.";i:8;s:198:"They have to steer the board to make decisions in the companys best interests make sure that all the important topics are discussed and for how long and move the meeting forward with momentum so as.";i:9;s:26:"Generally the AOA of a Co.";i:10;s:244:"Provides that the chairman of the board shall preside over the General Meetings as the chairman and it may also provide for the manner and procedure for the election of the chairman22 If the board has appointed a chairman and the AOA of the Co.";i:11;s:24:"CHAIRMAN OF THE MEETING.";i:12;s:291:"The Chairman of the board of directors of the General Partner or if there is no Chairman or if he is absent then the President or a Vice-President of the General Partner or any other Person who is present and has been chosen by means of an Ordinary Resolution shall preside over the meeting.";i:13;s:84:"The Chairman of the Board acts as the main liaison between the board and management.";i:14;s:132:"The person who fills this role is valuable during crisis situations in dealing with external groups such as investors and the media.";i:15;s:35:"Overall an independent board chair.";i:16;s:327:"Every company should have a chairman for the meetings of the board1Where the chairman of the board is an non-executive director then at least one-third of the board should comprise of independent directors and in case he is an executive director then at least one half of the board should comprise of the independent directors.";i:17;s:219:"OPENING STATEMENT BY THE CHAIR OF THE BOARD OF GOVERNORS Your Excellencies Distinguished Governors President Ladies and Gentlemen It is with great pleasure that I welcome you to the 22nd EBRD Annual Meeting in Istanbul.";i:18;s:96:"I feel very privileged to chair this Meeting of the EBRD in the great city of Istanbul which is.";i:19;s:257:"A Board Meeting is a formal meeting of the board of directors of an organization and any invited guests held at definite intervals and as needed to review performance consider policy issues address major problems and perform the legal business of the board.";i:20;s:116:"Presided over by a chairperson of the organization the quorum rules and responsibilities for board meetings will be.";i:21;s:52:"Running a board meeting can be a complicated affair.";i:22;s:225:"Whether you are the board chair worrying about maintaining focus and facilitating engagement or the board liaison preoccupied with the difficulties of planning the meeting and creating board books board meetings involve many.";i:23;s:49:"1 Planning to chair a board of directors meeting.";i:24;s:130:"Start planning a board meeting by setting a meeting goal and learning what the board of directors expects of you as meeting chair.";i:25;s:78:"Discuss these points with each board member separately to collect information.";i:26;s:101:"Next highlight the meeting goal and use board-member feedback to set the meeting procedure and rules.";i:27;s:416:"The chairman if any of the board of directors or in his absence some other director nominated by the directors shall preside as chairman of the meeting but if neither the chairman nor such other director if any be present within fifteen minutes after the time appointed for holding the meeting and willing to act the directors present shall elect one of their number to be chairman and if there is only one director.";i:28;s:122:"It provides that the Chairperson of the board if any shall preside as chairperson at every general meeting of the company.";i:29;s:263:"Where there is no such Chairperson or if he is not present within 15 minutes after the time appointed for holding the meeting or is unwilling to act as Chairperson of the meeting the directors present shall elect one of directors to be Chairperson of the meeting.";i:30;s:398:"Whilst the Chairman and Chief Executive are collectively responsible for the leadership of the Group and for promoting the highest standards of integrity and probity there is a clear and effective division of accountability and responsibility between the Chairman and the Chief Executive and each plays a distinctive role but complementing each other to ensure that there is a balance of power and.";i:31;s:236:"Chairman means the Chairman of the Board or the Chairman appointed or elected for a Meeting Hence the chairman of general meeting can be either chairman of board or any member as may be selected by members themselves during the meeting.";i:32;s:167:"As a matter of convention the chairman of the meeting of the Board of Directors is a member on all the Board committees and he presides over all the committee meeting.";i:33;s:162:"However the above provision of Regulation 78 or any corresponding provision in the articles of any company shall govern the appointment of the committee chairman.";i:34;s:54:"The main features of the role of Chair are as follows.";i:35;s:187:"As well as being Chair of the board they expected to act as the companys leading representative which will involve the presentation of the companys aims and policies to the outside world.";i:36;s:21:"To take the chair at.";}}